            "body": "<p>戊戌六君子的血,没能唤醒四万万中国人;</p><p>六四学生的血,同样没能唤醒十一亿中国人;<em><br></em></p><p>绝大多数的中国人,除非用他们自己的血,否则是唤不醒的!</p><p><img src=\"/uploads/ueditor/20180915/1536984045247063.jpg\" title=\"1536984045247063.jpg\" alt=\"01.jpg\"><img src=\"/uploads/ueditor/20180915/1536984116702342.jpg\" title=\"1536984116702342.jpg\" alt=\"02.jpg\"><img src=\"/uploads/ueditor/20180915/1536984154650887.jpg\" title=\"1536984154650887.jpg\" alt=\"03.jpg\"><img src=\"/uploads/ueditor/20180915/1536984204379124.jpg\" title=\"1536984204379124.jpg\" alt=\"04.jpg\"></p>",
